      "answer": "6.3.3 During the term of this Agreement and after its expiration or termination, you shall not directly or indirectly contest the validity of, or our ownership of the Proprietary Marks, nor take any other action which may tend to jeopardize our or our affiliate's interest therein, or our right to use and to license others to use the Proprietary Marks.",
